<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>食事と栄養</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="dashboard.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>食事と栄養</h1>
        <a href="dashboard.html" class="back-link">ダッシュボードに戻る</a>
    </header>

    <main class="dashboard-grid">
        <div class="health-card card-nutrition">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3>今日の栄養バランス</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="chart-container-bar">
                    <canvas id="nutritionChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="health-card card-suggestion">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3 id="suggestion-message">今日の献立提案</h3>
            </div>
            <div id="recipe-suggestions" class="card-body recipe-container">
                <p>おすすめの献立を読み込んでいます...</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="nutrition.js"></script>
</body>
</html>